      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/637702844_18566653849034732_7571132777879894508_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s640x640_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=108&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgzNjI2MjI5OTMzNDQ3NjIyNDE4NTY2NjUzODQ2MDM0NzMy.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjY3MngxMTk0LnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=dKp_fjPuMEEQ7kNvwF2fv5r&amp;_nc_oc=AdpOOA68V9CaY9lN-4Z5l3uEDpPp63NVK5c7r4zxm2h7H0BPyCls-gtQGfxCkg9cQis&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=ZZzHLdg3CN0g7if2sI-U_Q&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwVYz7nUCzNjCykvvr8WXbsFq13MLRAsBgQ-IVtfCxLpg&amp;oe=69C91478" alt="Instagram billede fra @kentbrantlenite" /></p><p><strong>@kentbrantlenite</strong></p><p>I do the large majority of my photography with adapted lenses. So naturally it&#x27;s my go-to when I get my hands on any camera. My old GoPro Hero 3 wasn&#x27;t very useful otherwise. I had to attach a screen and battery bank to it just to take these shaky videos. It&#x27;s also the foggiest day in the history of mankind 🤷<br/>
